## Description
<h1>TimeStretcherPlus</h1>
<p>The TimeStretcherPlus atom package comes with a TimeStretcher node default setting that adds a "Set To Current Time" UserControl button to the node. Also, when a TimeStretcher node is added to a Fusion comp, the "SourceTime" value is automatically set to the current time.</p>
